snippet.title: FOX 5 Washington DC
snippet.description:
The official YouTube home for FOX 5 DC, WTTG-TV in Washington, D.C.  We bring you breaking news, local stories from around D.C., Maryland and Virginia, and the videos from around the D.C. region that you want to see most!  

Connect with us for news updates 24/7 at www.fox5dc.com. You'll also find us on Twitter @fox5dc, and on Facebook: FOX 5 DC. We're also on Instagram @fox5dc. Join us there.  

If you've got a news tip to share with us, please email us at fox5tips@foxtv.com. We want to hear from you!
